results.name: a(n) = A002487(n^2).
comment: Conjecture: For all i >= 0, j >= 0: A103391(1+i) = A103391(1+j) => a(i) = a(j). This would be an implication of observation made at A286377, which has been checked up to n=2048. See also A286378.
